snippet.title: Fabián C. Barrio
snippet.description:
Una digna mezcla de Paulo Coelho, el cuñado de la barra del bar, y Torbe. El viejo lesbiano que chilla encaramado en su roca en mitad del mar. El fachirulo heteropatriarca opresor que todos estaban esperando. Orgulloso mediocre. Bardo, escritor y viajero chipriota. Overlander majestuoso y migrante. Hablo para vivir. Soy el Alcalde.  

Atención a la clasificación de los vídeos, por favor: 

🟢 Vídeos para todos los públicos. 
🟡 Vídeos con contenido político leve, que podrían resultarle levemente molestos. Mi consejo es que no los vea, pero posiblemente no le provoquen demasiada ansiedad. 
🔴 Vídeos altamente polémicos, sólo para fachafrancopantanos. NO LOS VEA si sus ideas políticas son firmes. REPITO, NO LOS VEA si es usted incapaz de ser crítico con los de su bando.

snippet.title: Rebel News
snippet.description:
Telling the other side of the story. 

We follow the facts wherever they may lead — even if that conflicts with the official narrative of the establishment.

We see that the mainstream media doesn't admit to their own political bias, and they pretend to be neutral providers of the news when they are anything but.

At Rebel News we fearlessly take on that “Media Party”. We tell it like it is, and we examine the world from a different perspective — a side of the story you won't get anywhere else.

Unlike most of our competitors, we don't take money from any government. We depend on viewers like you to crowdfunded our journalism. It’s harder to run a company that way. But it’s the only way to be free from editorial interference behind the scenes.

Rebel News is one of the few media outlets that has the power, freedom, and reach to challenge the views presented in the mainstream media.

For more about Rebel News, see our website: https://www.rebelnews.com/about

snippet.title: The Economic Times
snippet.description:
A Times Internet Product  

The Economic Times is an English-language Indian daily newspaper published by the Bennett, Coleman & Co. Ltd., more popularly known as The Times Group. 

The Economic Times, started in 1961, is Asia's largest and among the world's top 3 English Business dailies. Published simultaneously from 12 cities - Mumbai, Bangalore, Delhi, Chennai, Kolkata, Lucknow, Hyderabad, Jaipur, Ahmedabad, Nagpur, Chandigarh and Pune.

www.economictimes.com is India's No. 1 business and financial news website. Launched in 1999, economictimes.com offers live 24x7 coverage of economy, business and markets from around the world, with special focus on India.

The Times Group is India's most diversified media company with power brands across publishing, television, internet, radio and outdoor domains. 

To subscribe, go to: http://www.youtube.com/TheEconomicTimes?sub_confirmation=1
For more videos visit our website - http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/TV

At Queen Mary University of London, we believe that a diversity of ideas helps us achieve
the previously unthinkable.

Throughout our history, we’ve fostered social justice and improved lives through academic excellence. And we continue to live and breathe this spirit today, not because it’s simply ‘the right thing to do’ but for what it helps us achieve and the intellectual brilliance it delivers.

We continue to embrace diversity of thought and opinion in everything we do, in the belief that when views collide, disciplines interact, and perspectives intersect, truly original thought takes form.

snippet.title: DW News
snippet.description:
Journalism that’s Made for Minds. Follow us for global news and analysis from the heart of Europe. DW News delivers the world's breaking news while going deep beneath the surface of what's going on. Correspondents on the ground and in the studio provide their detailed analysis and insights on issues that affect our viewers. 

Deutsche Welle is Germany’s international broadcaster, producing content in 30 languages. We independently report social, political and economic developments in Germany and Europe, incorporating both German and other perspectives. DW hopes to promote understanding between different cultures and peoples. 

While funded by the German government, the work of DW is regulated by the Deutsche Welle Act (http://p.dw.com/p/17MtP), meaning content is always independent of government influence. 

We ask that you please keep comments and discussions on this channel clean and respectful. For further information please click the 'DW Netiquette' link below.

snippet.title: TRT World
snippet.description:
At TRT World we're building a global community focused around change. We’re looking beyond the headlines to drive meaningful conversations that empower. We want to connect people across the globe to issues that matter. We explore the reality behind the hashtags and the people behind the statistics. We will seek to unpack the issues behind each story.

By placing the human at the heart of each story we hope to promote a global conscience that provokes moral reactions - revealing a deeper understanding of the diversity of the lives around us.

Subscribe to our channel for all our latest in-depth, on the ground reporting from around the world.

snippet.title: m j murcott
snippet.description: Science, fiction and thought provoking ideas. With a little imagination and inventiveness it is possible to improve the world. If you like what you find here feel free to share it with your friends, if you think there is a topic I should cover feel free to comment, I am always looking for new subjects. From the 5th Feb 2016  I have been using an upgraded camera, however due to the large number of videos using the older equipment these will still be retained even if the quality isn't as good. Recent changes in lighting have again improved the videos so they look less "ghostly" as one person described it. The channels page now features "the toast train" a podcast I did a couple of interviews on which can be found on the live section of their channel.

snippet.title: euronews
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official Euronews YouTube channel!

Around the clock, our team of 500 journalists of more than 30 different nationalities gathers news with impartial perspective, beyond the headlines content and voices from across Europe and the world. Our YouTube channel has all this and more, bringing you selected and original content from the world's most trusted news source.

Our mission is to empower people to form their own opinion. We trust in people’s intelligence and ability to make up their own mind and seek to provide our audience with the greatest diversity of viewpoints through journalism that is unapologetically impartial. We don’t trade in bias and outrage, we focus on facts, ideas, and solutions. We believe all views matter.

snippet.title: UCL
snippet.description:
UCL (University College London) is consistently ranked among the world's top ten universities (QS World University Rankings 2010 - 2025). Our excellence extends across all academic disciplines, from one of the world's foremost centres for research and teaching in the biological sciences to world-renowned centres for architecture (The Bartlett), education (IOE, Faculty of Education and Society) and fine art (Slade School of Fine Art). 

UCL is London's leading multidisciplinary university, with more than 16,000 staff and 51,000 students from 150 different countries. Founded in 1826 in the heart of London, UCL was the first university in England to welcome students of any religion and the first to welcome women on equal terms with men. 

UCL Minds brings together UCL’s knowledge, insights, and ideas through events, activities, and digital content open to everyone. Find out what’s on UCL Minds: www.ucl.ac.uk/minds

snippet.title: Comipoop
snippet.description:
Scope of this channel is to promote a new form of popular art...the Comipoop!
What is a Comipoop?
A comipoop (combination of the words Comic and poop...or poo) is a modern voulgar pop art that mixes pieces of any kind of comics gathered from real comic books (scissors work), without any modification made via software tools like photoshop, with audio records gathered from any particular source. A comipoop can be everything and nothing...its pure imagination!
This channel also contains some other funny videos that I started to make just to understand how Youtube works...but it will be mainly focused on the comipoop.

All the videos are made by using real comic books. Scissors and lot of patience in order to put together a funny comipoop story.

All the comics come from DC Comics and Marvel till now.

snippet.title: Fomo Finance
snippet.description:
Herzlich Wilkommen!
Auf unserem Youtube-Kanal, sowie unserer Website und Facebook-Site, veröffentlichen wir regelmäßig Videos und Artikel rund um die Themen Traden und Investieren.
Wir haben uns dabei auf folgende Gebiete spezialisiert:

- Optionen/Optionshandel
- Futures-Handel
- Technische Analyse
- Intermarketanalyse
- Commitments Of Traders
- passives Investieren mit ETFs

Einerseits findes Du Lerninhalte zu den genannten Themen; andererseits besprechen und analysieren wir regelmäßig das aktuelle Marktgeschehen und zeigen, worauf wir in unserem täglichen Handel achten und stellen gelegentlich eigene Trades vor.

Wir sind davon überzeugt, dass profitabler Börsenhandel erlernbar ist. Es gibt jedoch viel zu viele "Schaufelverkäufer", insb. auch auf den Sozialen Medien, die einem das Blaue vom Himmel versprechen. 
Uns ist es deshalb wichtig, Dir einen realistischen Einblick in unseren täglichen Handel zu geben, und zu zeigen was möglich ist, und was nicht.

snippet.title: euronews (in Italiano)
snippet.description:
Benvenuti al canale Youtube ufficiale di Euronews! 

Tutti i giorni, a tutte le ore, la nostra squadra di 500 giornalisti provenienti da oltre 30 Paesi lavora per raccontarvi l'Europa con assoluta imparzialità. Su questo canale trovate una selezione dei migliori contenuti della TV europea per eccellenza. 

La nostra missione è quella di dare alle persone la possibilità di formarsi una propria opinione. Confidiamo nell'intelligenza e nella capacità delle persone di decidere da sole e cerchiamo di fornire al nostro pubblico la più grande diversità di punti di vista attraverso un giornalismo imparziale.
Ci concentriamo su fatti, idee e soluzioni.
Crediamo che tutti i punti di vista siano importanti.

Euronews è nato dalla volontà di creare un canale d'informazione europeo indipendente. Essendo l'unico media internazionale con una prospettiva europea, Euronews è il luogo a cui si rivolge il mondo per ascoltare ciò che l'Europa ha da dire.

snippet.title: Kiel Institute for the World Economy
snippet.description:
The Kiel Institute is an international center for research in global economic affairs, economic policy consulting, and economic education. The Institute engages especially in creating solutions to urgent problems in global economic affairs. On basis of its research, the Institute advises decision-takers in policy, business, and society and informs the broader public about important developments in international economic policy.
-- 
Das Institut für Weltwirtschaft an der Universität Kiel (IfW) ist eines der großen Zentren weltwirtschaftlicher Forschung, wirtschaftspolitischer Beratung und ökonomischer Ausbildung. Das Institut sieht seine Hauptaufgabe in der Erforschung innovativer Lösungsansätze für drängende weltwirtschaftliche Probleme. Auf Basis dieser Forschungsarbeiten berät es Entscheidungsträger in Politik, Wirtschaft und Gesellschaft und informiert die interessierte Öffentlichkeit über wichtige wirtschaftspolitische Zusammenhänge.

snippet.title: Österreichische Gesellschaft für Europapolitik
snippet.description:
Die Österreichische Gesellschaft für Europapolitik (ÖGfE) ist ein parteipolitisch unabhängiger Verein
auf sozialpartnerschaftlicher Basis.

Wir informieren über europäische Integration und stehen für einen offenen Dialog über aktuelle europapolitische Fragen und deren Relevanz für Österreich. Wir verfügen über langjährige Erfahrung in Bezug auf die Förderung europäischer Debatten und agieren als Katalysator zur Verbreitung von europapolitischen Informationen und Analysen. Die ÖGfE wurde im Jahr 1991 gegründet und wird finanziert und gebildet von den österreichischen Sozialpartnern und der Oesterreichischen Nationalbank.

snippet.title: University of Birmingham
snippet.description:
The University of Birmingham is one of the most popular UK universities, offering diverse opportunities for study and research.

From 1900 to the present day, the University of Birmingham has been at the forefront of both national and international research, leading the way in making ground-breaking progress in areas that span industries such as gene structure, medicine, space research and communications.
We are changing how the world works. 

A global reputation, quality learning and teaching, excellent facilities, a stunning campus and great city are some of the reasons making Birmingham a great place to study and live.

snippet.title: TG2000
snippet.description:
Tutti i giorni dal lunedì alla domenica notiziari quotidiani e rubriche di approfondimento. Servizi, interviste, inviati in Italia e nel mondo per raccontare quel che accade e anticipare i grandi eventi, con particolare attenzione alla realtà meno illuminata dai grandi media. Grande attenzione all’affidabilità delle fonti con uno stile non aggressivo; il racconto si affida a uno sguardo diverso, più umano. L’attività del Papa e della Chiesa viene raccontata non per dovere istituzionale ma perché nelle parole e nei gesti di Francesco passa tutti i giorni un contenuto esistenziale che intercetta le domande più importanti di ogni uomo sul senso della vita. Le notizie vengono approfondite con analisi e commenti, per aiutare i telespettatori a discernere e a capire oltre i titoli che scorrono veloci in rete. Cinque edizioni al giorno dal lunedì al sabato: ore 12, 18.30 e 20.45 e due FLASH alle 8.30 e alle 14.55. E due edizioni la domenica ore 18.30 e 20.45.
Direttore: Vincenzo Morgante

localized.description:
Tutti i giorni dal lunedì alla domenica notiziari quotidiani e rubriche di approfondimento. Servizi, interviste, inviati in Italia e nel mondo per raccontare quel che accade e anticipare i grandi eventi, con particolare attenzione alla realtà meno illuminata dai grandi media. Grande attenzione all’affidabilità delle fonti con uno stile non aggressivo; il racconto si affida a uno sguardo diverso, più umano. L’attività del Papa e della Chiesa viene raccontata non per dovere istituzionale ma perché nelle parole e nei gesti di Francesco passa tutti i giorni un contenuto esistenziale che intercetta le domande più importanti di ogni uomo sul senso della vita. Le notizie vengono approfondite con analisi e commenti, per aiutare i telespettatori a discernere e a capire oltre i titoli che scorrono veloci in rete. Cinque edizioni al giorno dal lunedì al sabato: ore 12, 18.30 e 20.45 e due FLASH alle 8.30 e alle 14.55. E due edizioni la domenica ore 18.30 e 20.45.
Direttore: Vincenzo Morgante

snippet.title: UKspreadbetting
snippet.description:
🔴 Trading is Risky! 70% to 89% of retail investors lose money!  Financial-Spread-Betting.com is where betting and finance meets, on the trading floor.  This is a place where we can inform, and educate little, and hopefully entertain a little too.

Spread betting is an efficient way to trade the financial markets as you pay no stamp duty or CGT on any profits you make. This is because the activity is regulated as gambling, as opposed to investing, which means spread traders don't normally pay taxes on their winnings.  The flipside of this is that with spread betting you cannot offset losses against your profits for capital gains tax purposes.

Leverage can amplify both your gains and losses since they are calculated based on the total exposure of the trade, not merely the margin needed to initiate it. Consequently, losses and profits could far outweigh your margin, so always ensure you’re trading within your means.

snippet.title: Incorrigible Forever
snippet.description:
"Everyone is entitled to their own opinion but not their own facts"

Divisive inequality & social injustice are spreading as a consequence of our collective political choices. Unless you own a tin hat, you'd probably choose to consign poverty, racism and sexism to history & to reverse climate change  - so why haven't you? We are constantly misled about the causes of injustice & inequality by media groups with political agendas & governments who manufacture crises as a means of distraction - party strategists call it a 'dead cat' distraction. 

Human ingenuity allows us to formulate solutions to complex social, economic & scientific problems but our personal greed is why we regularly fail, often by design, to implement them. This blog examines these issues & key questions such as: Does distributing political power on the basis of wealth serve our society or prevent our progress? & Why do we accept the media's open use of half-truths & lies to manipulate our democracy?

China Global Television Network, or CGTN, is an international media organization launched on December 31, 2016. It aims to provide global audiences with accurate and timely news coverage as well as rich audiovisual services, promoting communication and understanding between China and the world, and enhancing cultural exchanges and mutual trust between China and other countries. 

Headquartered in Beijing, CGTN has three production centers, located in Nairobi, Washington D.C. and London, all staffed with international professionals from around the world.

Adhering to the principles of objectivity, rationality and balance in reporting, CGTN endeavors to present information from diverse perspectives.

snippet.title: One Minute Economics
snippet.description:
My name is Andrei Polgar, I'm a PhD economist who loves teaching through videos, books or anything else that works! :)

To support the channel, please give me a minute (see what I did there?) of your time by visiting OneMinuteEconomics.com and reading my message.

Bitcoin donations: bc1qmnfwn4p3gdu8kl2zwh6gge0fq6w3j2qyv3f350

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/oneminuteeconomics

My first book, Wealth Management 2.0 (through which I do my best to help people manage their wealth properly):

https://www.amazon.com/Wealth-Management-2-0-Financial-Professionals-ebook/dp/B01I1WA2BK

My second book, the Wall Street Journal and USA Today bestseller The Age of Anomaly (through which I help people prepare for financial calamities and become more financially resilient in general):

https://www.amazon.com/Age-Anomaly-Spotting-Financial-Uncertainty-ebook/dp/B078SYL5YS

And book #3, The Reasonable Case for Bitcoin: 

https://www.amazon.com/Reasonable-Case-Bitcoin-Andrei-Polgar-ebook/dp/B09G6Z45QB

snippet.title: Rev Brother Sean Bradley
snippet.description:
In a nutshell, when we reach the crossroads of our life, so many times we sense a deep inner longing within our heart to reflect on why I am here and what my life’s purposes are……..
If you are still on that road of self discovery and would like to test whether or not you have a monastic calling to live as a modern day lay monastic without having to leave family or friends, then seek divine guidance within your heart-then honor it and explore the choices right for your spiritual pathway. Why miss this golden opportunity today.
Pax et Bonum
Brother Sean
Founder and Abbott of the TCOSF

snippet.title: euronews (deutsch)
snippet.description:
Willkommen auf dem offiziellen Euronews YouTube-Kanal!  

Rund um die Uhr produziert unser Team von 500 Journalisten mit mehr als 30 verschiedenen Nationalitäten möglichst objektive Nachrichten mit Stimmen aus ganz Europa und der Welt. Unser YouTube-Kanal bietet ausgewählte und originelle Beiträge von Europas führendem internationalen Nachrichten-TV.

Euronews ermöglicht es, sich eine eigene Meinung zu bilden. Wir vertrauen auf die Intelligenz und die Fähigkeit der Menschen und versuchen unserem Publikum durch einen unparteiischen Journalismus, eine Vielfalt von Standpunkten aufzuzeigen.
Euronews berichtet unvoreingenommen und sachlich, wir konzentrieren uns auf Fakten, Ideen und Lösungen.
Wir sind überzeugt, dass alle Ansichten zählen.

Euronews ist aus dem Willen heraus entstanden, einen starken unabhängigen europäischen Nachrichtensender zu schaffen. Als einziges internationales Nachrichtenmedium mit einem europäischen Blickwinkel kann man auf Euronews erfahren, was Europa bewegt.

snippet.title: RUSHY 01
snippet.description:
This is the official RUSHY 01 YouTube channel! 
Hello my name is Ryan and welcome to my YouTube channel.  
I upload multiple types of content including education based videos, vlogs, self-improvement & advice videos, gaming videos, travel videos, automotive videos, hair loss videos, Q&A videos, footwear reviews, eating challenges and even social experiments.  
I also upload shorts and l sometimes host live streams as well.  
I currently upload 1 new video every month.  
None of my videos are age restricted.
I have playlists grouping videos with simular topics together making them easier to find.  
Feel free to interact by leaving a comment on my videos & posts, I will see and respond/react to every comment.
If you've subscribed, thank you and welcome, I really appreciate it and I hope you enjoy the content I have created and will continue to create.

snippet.title: Andreas G. Wolff, MA (International Journalism)
snippet.description:
This is an “Indigenous and Minority Peoples’ Channel” with a focus on language learning and revitalisation of minority languages. Occasionally it may feature some other stuff I’m involved in. 

A BBC correspondent and video journalist in my day job, based in the Scottish Highlands, but also reporting internationally. Contributed packages and lives to the BBC News Channel, BBC SCOTLAND and BBC ALBA as well as BBC radio e.g. about Brexit, the Paris terrorist attacks and the Conclave. Regular contributor to German public service broadcasters Deutsche Welle TV  and Deutschlandradio. 

A language expert – fluent in English, German, Spanish, Scottish Gaelic, French and Italian and getting by in Portuguese, Russian and Irish. Now learning Mandarin, Swedish and Northern Frisian (Fering). President and Gaelic tutor of the Taynuilt Gaelic Choir with a BA (Hons) in Scottish Gaelic. Was a director of Oban Hospice in charge of PR for 6 years.
